snippet.title: SPEED DREAMS - Sixties Superspeed at Forza
snippet.description:
We have just released our new Release Candidate for version 2.3.0, and among its many new features is the inclusion of the Murasama 37A from the 1967 Grand Prix Category. This car is based on the F1-67 Honda RA273 openwheeler.

The track is our old familiar Forza, which as you know is our replica of the mythical Monza. We hope you like it.

If you want to enjoy this car you can download the Release Candidate of our next version 2.3.0. You have more info about the RC in this new in our official website: 
https://www.speed-dreams.net/en/new-2-3-0-release-candidate/

You can find this game and more info about this Open Source project on:
https://www.speed-dreams.net 

Music by:
Riptide - Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)

http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
